short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Four Seasons - the right theme for the right season

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Four Seasons is a New-Tab extension with the right mood for the current season

With Four Seasons, you get a wonderful season wallpaper based on the current season. You can also choose the current season and the background will update accordingly.

By clicking the "Add to Chrome" button you hereby agree to installing this Chrome extension, as well as its Search services, Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.

The Search features within this extension will be provided by Microsoft Bing.

For more information please visit https://seasons-bg.com
